reviewText: great combo set. Nice to have classic movies in great condition.
Hilarious! I don't remember the Blazzing Saddles movie being so in-PC.....Love it
Perfect gift for my funny guy
Great collection of funny movies all in one place!

I loved these movies way back when I first watched them.  However, I do not remember any foul language in them. The ones i have seem so far, have BAD language in them. The DVD is in great shape. But would have not ordered if I knew it had foul language in them. So I am very disappointed about this. These are not the family movies I remember.

Started with Blazing Saddles. One heck of a movie. 5 dvds of the best comedies.
It should be in everyone's collection.
